s internal consistency reliability - how closely related your scale items a=
re as a group. It tells you whether your questionnaire items consistently m=
easure the same underlying construct. Higher values indicate items are high=
ly intercorrelated.</div></div></div><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEn=
